name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jonathan T. MOORE, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jonathan T. MOORE, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 6th day of January, 2014, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. See Pa.R.Crim.P. 122(B)(2). Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jonathan T. MOORE, Petitioner.

Jan. 6, 2014.
